assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: TECHNOLOGIES, Inc. provides IT solutions primarily in the areas of AI and entertainment software fields in Japan. The company designs, develops, and provides various software, such as autonomous driving applications for automobile manufacturers; AI learning teaching materials with robots for children; automotive remote control systems that enables remote control of vehicles for anti-theft purposes; LIVE distribution apps; and projection mapping solutions. It also offers 3D signage/operation authentication systems; Smile Up, an entertainment software; jewelry AR applications; financial automatic trading systems; and virtual currency payment systems. In addition, the company engages in planning, video, and control software production comprising game machine development. Further, the company develops and offers SaaS based solutions for small and medium-sized temporary staffing companies. Additionally, it is involved in the HD business; and hardware and software construction, as well as provision of services related to AI and SaaS. The company was formerly known as BEL AIR Co., Ltd. and changed its name to TECHNOLOGIES, Inc. in 2022. TECHNOLOGIES, Inc. was incorporated in 2014 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan.
